#MEM id=responsive-design source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/design-and-build/responsive-design/SKILL.md
M|responsive-design|name: responsive-design
M|responsive-design|description: Mia's responsive design framework for YVON's glass morphism system. Covers breakpoints, mobile glass adaptations, touch targets, fluid typography, and the responsive pass checklist for ea
M|responsive-design|version: 1.0.0
M|responsive-design|YVON's glass morphism design system (V1–V4 containers, backdrop-blur, layered gradients) was built desktop-first. Mobile requires deliberate adaptation — backdrop-blur is GPU-expensive on mobile, glas
M|responsive-design|- Any new screen build
M|responsive-design|- Any existing screen responsive pass (flagged in ses.md)
M|responsive-design|- When a component uses `backdrop-filter`, `glass-*` class, or layered gradient background
M|responsive-design|- Before any screen is marked "done" in Diana's sprint tracking
M|responsive-design|```css
M|responsive-design|/* globals.css — use these exact custom properties */
M|responsive-design|--bp-mobile:  480px   /* small phones */
M|responsive-design|--bp-tablet:  768px   /* tablets and large phones landscape */
M|responsive-design|--bp-desktop: 1024px  /* desktop default */
M|responsive-design|--bp-wide:    1280px  /* wide desktop */
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|Tailwind equivalents: `sm: (640)`, `md: (768)`, `lg: (1024)`, `xl: (1280)`.
M|responsive-design|**Mobile-first rule:** Base CSS = mobile. Augment with `md:` and `lg:` breakpoints. Never write desktop-first and try to override down.
M|responsive-design|| Property | Desktop | Mobile (< 768px) |
M|responsive-design||----------|---------|-----------------|
M|responsive-design|| `backdrop-blur` | `blur(20px)` | `blur(8px)` — GPU performance |
M|responsive-design|| Glass opacity | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` | `rgba(255,255,255,0.12)` — more visible on small screens |
M|responsive-design|| Border radius | `16–24px` | `12px` — tighter on small viewport |
M|responsive-design|| Padding (glass card) | `24px` | `16px` |
M|responsive-design|| Box shadow depth | Full 3-layer | Single layer — mobile doesn't need depth |
M|responsive-design|| `border: 1px solid rgba(...)` | Keep | Keep — defines container edge clearly |
M|responsive-design|**Disable backdrop-blur completely on screens narrower than 380px.** Use a solid background fallback.
M|responsive-design|All interactive elements on mobile MUST meet:
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|Minimum touch target: 44px × 44px (Apple HIG) / 48dp × 48dp (Material)
M|responsive-design|Spacing between adjacent targets: ≥ 8px
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|Common failures in YVON:
M|responsive-design|- Tab buttons in CEO dashboard (often < 32px tall) → add `min-h-[44px]` on mobile
M|responsive-design|- Icon buttons in NavBar → ensure `p-3` minimum
M|responsive-design|- Small KPI delta badges with `onClick` → wrap in a larger hit area
M|responsive-design|YVON uses large display fonts for KPIs and section headers. These must scale:
M|responsive-design|| Element | Desktop | Mobile |
M|responsive-design||---------|---------|--------|
M|responsive-design|| KPI values (52px) | `text-[52px]` | `text-[32px]` |
M|responsive-design|| Page title (48px) | `text-[48px]` | `text-[28px]` |
M|responsive-design|| Section labels (12px) | `text-[12px]` | `text-[12px]` — do not reduce further |
M|responsive-design|| Body text (14px) | `text-[14px]` | `text-[14px]` — floor, do not reduce |
M|responsive-design|Use `clamp()` for fluid scaling where the range is smooth:
M|responsive-design|```css
M|responsive-design|font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 52px);  /* scales from 28px to 52px */
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|Before any screen is marked complete, run this checklist at 375px, 768px, and 1280px:
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|□ No horizontal scroll at any breakpoint
M|responsive-design|□ Glass containers visible (not invisible at < 768px)
M|responsive-design|□ Touch targets ≥ 44px for all interactive elements
M|responsive-design|□ Text does not overflow glass card bounds
M|responsive-design|□ Navigation is accessible (mobile menu or collapsed state)
M|responsive-design|□ KPI values do not clip at 375px
M|responsive-design|□ Scrollable lists have visible scroll indicator on touch
M|responsive-design|□ No fixed-width elements wider than 100vw
M|responsive-design|□ backdrop-blur disabled or reduced at < 768px
M|responsive-design|□ All images use next/image with responsive sizes prop
M|responsive-design|```
M|responsive-design|Fail any item → fix before marking done.
M|responsive-design|| Screen | Known mobile issues | Fix |
M|responsive-design||--------|--------------------|----|
M|responsive-design|| CEO Command Dashboard | Tab row overflows on 375px | Horizontal scroll on tabs + `scroll-snap-x` |
M|responsive-design|| anl | Multi-column KPI strip collapses | Stack to 1-col grid below `md:` |
M|responsive-design|| War Room | Chat bubbles overflow glass container | `max-w-[calc(100%-32px)]` on message cards |
M|responsive-design|| cp | Wide data tables | `overflow-x-auto` wrapper + `min-w-[600px]` on table |